<tr>
<td>HCPro, Inc. has furthered its expansion into the nursing information delivery sector by acquiring Orlando-based Bandido Books, a publisher of clinical and non-clinical nursing information. HCPro will still be offering many of Bandido's books. For a complete list, please see the list of products below.
<p>For more information, call HCPro's Customer Service at <b>800/650-6787</b> or e-mail at <b><a href="mailto:customerservice@hcpro.com">customerservice@hcpro.com</a></b>. You may also visit HCPro's Web site at <b><a href="http://www.hcpro.com">www.hcpro.com</a></b>.
</td>
</tr>
