<table style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial" width="700">
<tr>
<td colspan="2" align="center"><b style="font-size: 12pt">Stressed Out Series</b>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top">
<img src="http://images.hcpro.com/promos/nursing_school.gif">
</td>
<td><p><a href="http://www.hcmarketplace.com/Add.cfm?ic=4046-9577&s=EBANDIDO"><b>Stressed Out About Nursing School! An Insider's Guide to Success</b></a> <b style="color: #ff0000">$29.95</b> <br />(160 pages).  </p>
<P>The authoritative student guide to one of the fastest growing, most in demand professions today!  Loaded with resources and written from a student's perspective.</p>
<p>This title guides the student through:
<ul>
<li>The rigors of making it into nursing school (applications, interviews, types of programs, is nursing for you? and more). </li>
<li>Surviving nursing school (what to expect, study tips, time management, the truth on clinicals, working and going to school plus tons more). </li>
<li>Life after school (acing the NCLEX, getting your dream job, what is nursing really like, salaries, specialization, grad school and much, much more!). </li>
<li>Helpful icons guide you through a myriad of resources and present expert advice on everything you ever wanted to know about nursing school.  The lighthearted manner makes it a joy to read.  </li>
</ul>
</p>
<p><a href="http://www.hcmarketplace.com/Add.cfm?ic=4046-9577&s=EBANDIDO">Click here to order</a>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top">
<br /><br /><img src="http://images.hcpro.com/promos/drug_math.gif">
</td>
<td>
<p><br/><br /><a href="http://www.hcmarketplace.com/Add.cfm?ic=4045-9576&s=EBANDIDO"><b>Stressed Out About Drug Math! Mastering Nursing Concepts</b></a> <b style="color: #ff0000">$29.95</b>
<br />(160 pages).
<P>Tackling drug dosage and calculation like you've never seen it before!  Includes a math review as well as advanced skills for measuring and administering medicines and intravenous solutions.</p>
<p>This title guides the student and clinician through:
<ul>
<li>A basic math review including working with decimals and fractions.</li> 
<li>Setting up equations and finding your method to solving medication problems. </li>
<li>Measuring systems, conversions, and drug administration (IVs, liquids, tablets, suppositories, injectables and more!).</li> 
<li>Solutions, dilutions, complex IV drug orders and other advanced topics. </li>
</ul></p>
<p>Let's face it, lots of us struggle with drug math. This book, through a friendly approach uses icons, examples (that &quot;walk you through&quot; a problem), and practice exercises to help you master drug math once and for all!  Filled with tips and expert advice to help protect you and your patients!  </p>
<p><a href="http://www.hcmarketplace.com/Add.cfm?ic=4045-9576&s=EBANDIDO">Click here to order</a>
</td>
</tr>
